+      <h1 style="font-size:1.6rem">Jeremy Xiang — Project Portfolio</h1>
+      <p>Six tested, documented quant &amp; systems projects by
+      <a href="https://jeremyxiang.com/">Jeremy Xiang</a>, CS + Economics at UW–Madison.</p>
+      <ul>
+        <li><a href="https://github.com/Jeremy-Xiang/stock-forecast-bench">stock-forecast-bench</a> — four OHLC forecasting models under strict walk-forward evaluation</li>
+        <li><a href="https://github.com/Jeremy-Xiang/alpha-factor-pipeline">alpha-factor-pipeline</a> — 17-factor alpha research pipeline with long-short backtest</li>
+        <li><a href="https://github.com/Jeremy-Xiang/multi-agent-analyst">multi-agent-analyst</a> — supervisor agent over three isolated subagents (Anthropic API)</li>
+        <li><a href="https://github.com/Jeremy-Xiang/screener-alerts">screener-alerts</a> — six event-semantics screening rules with pluggable notifiers</li>
+        <li><a href="https://github.com/Jeremy-Xiang/filings-assistant">filings-assistant</a> — citation-grounded RAG over financial filings</li>
+        <li><a href="https://github.com/Jeremy-Xiang/ticker-clustering">ticker-clustering</a> — clusters tickers by behavior, not sector label</li>
+      </ul>
+      <p>Related: <a href="https://thesis.jeremyxiang.com/">Thesis</a> ·
+      <a href="https://lab.jeremyxiang.com/">The Layering Lab</a></p>
